               Vectorized Filter: (_hyper_3_2_chunk.u = '90ec9e8e-4501-4232-9d03-6d7cf6132815'::uuid)
               Rows Removed by Filter: 999
               Bulk Decompression: true
               ->  Seq Scan on _timescaledb_internal._hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed (actual rows=1.00 loops=1)
                     Output: _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_count, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_min_1, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_max_1, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_v2_first_x, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_v2_last_x, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed.x, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed.value, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed.regress-test-bloom_u, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed.u, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_v2_min_ts, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed._ts_meta_v2_max_ts, _hyper_3_2_chunk_compressed.ts
